messages.messageBody:
Osprey is releasing 2 new Naval warefare books, " Fighting ships of the Far East" Vol.1 and Vol 2.
Volume one is China and S E Asia
Volume two is Korea and Japan
Vol. 1 is set for a 2002 release and 2003 for vol. 2. Both by Stephen Turnbull.
